[Cuba has received deserved international recognition for being the 1st overseas government to send doctors in West Africa, but it comes to mind that they could have had training in the relevant foreign language and medical terms before leaving Cuba, or while they have been waiting in-country. Their 6-month deployment ends in March 2015. - Mod.JW]

